<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Web Development Bootcamp Landing Page</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Become a job-ready web developer in 12 weeks with live mentorship, real projects, placement support, and a portfolio-first curriculum." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f172a" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://api.fontshare.com" />
  <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=general-sans@400,500,600,700&f[]=cabinet-grotesk@500,700,800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root, [data-theme="light"] {
      --text-xs: clamp(0.75rem, 0.7rem + 0.25vw, 0.875rem);
      --text-sm: clamp(0.875rem, 0.8rem + 0.35vw, 1rem);
      --text-base: clamp(1rem, 0.95rem + 0.25vw, 1.125rem);
      --text-lg: clamp(1.125rem, 1rem + 0.75vw, 1.5rem);
      --text-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1.25vw, 2.25rem);
      --text-2xl: clamp(2.25rem, 1.3rem + 3vw, 4.5rem);

      --space-1: 0.25rem;
      --space-2: 0.5rem;
      --space-3: 0.75rem;
      --space-4: 1rem;
      --space-5: 1.25rem;
      --space-6: 1.5rem;
      --space-8: 2rem;
      --space-10: 2.5rem;
      --space-12: 3rem;
      --space-16: 4rem;
      --space-20: 5rem;

      --color-bg: #f6f7fb;
      --color-surface: #ffffff;
      --color-surface-2: #eef2ff;
      --color-surface-offset: #e8edf8;
      --color-border: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
      --color-text: #0f172a;
      --color-text-muted: #475569;
      --color-text-faint: #64748b;
      --color-primary: #2563eb;
      --color-primary-hover: #1d4ed8;
      --color-primary-soft: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.12);
      --color-accent: #0f172a;
      --color-success: #166534;
      --radius-sm: 0.5rem;
      --radius-md: 0.9rem;
      --radius-lg: 1.25rem;
      --radius-xl: 1.75rem;
      --shadow-sm: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      --shadow-md: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
      --font-body: 'General Sans', Inter, sans-serif;
      --font-display: 'Cabinet Grotesk', 'General Sans', sans-serif;
      --content: min(1120px, calc(100% - 2rem));
    }

    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --color-bg: #020617;
      --color-surface: #0f172a;
      --color-surface-2: #111c35;
      --color-surface-offset: #17233e;
      --color-border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
      --color-text: #e2e8f0;
      --color-text-muted: #cbd5e1;
      --color-text-faint: #94a3b8;
      --color-primary: #60a5fa;
      --color-primary-hover: #93c5fd;
      --color-primary-soft: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.14);
      --color-accent: #f8fafc;
      --color-success: #4ade80;
      --shadow-sm: 0 8px 24px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.35);
      --shadow-md: 0 18px 50px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.5);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--color-text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, var(--color-primary-soft), transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at left center, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08), transparent 20%),
        var(--color-bg);
    }
    img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    button, input, select, textarea { font: inherit; color: inherit; }
    button { cursor: pointer; border: none; background: none; }
    :focus-visible { outline: 3px solid var(--color-primary); outline-offset: 2px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm); }
    .skip-link {
      position: absolute; left: var(--space-4); top: -3rem; background: var(--color-primary); color: white;
      padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); z-index: 100;
    }
    .skip-link:focus { top: var(--space-4); }

    .container { width: var(--content); margin-inline: auto; }
    .section { padding: clamp(var(--space-12), 10vw, 6rem) 0; }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2); padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 999px; background: var(--color-surface);
      color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-xs); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .eyebrow::before { content: ""; width: 0.55rem; height: 0.55rem; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--color-primary); }
    .section-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      max-width: 16ch; margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-3);
    }
    .section-copy { color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 60ch; }

    .site-header {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 40; backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 82%, transparent); border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    .site-header.scrolled { border-color: var(--color-border); }
    .nav {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--space-4);
      min-height: 4.5rem;
    }
    .brand {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 2.35rem; height: 2.35rem; border-radius: 0.8rem; display: grid; place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), #38bdf8); color: white; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .brand-mark svg { width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem; }
    .nav-links {
      display: none; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-5); color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-3); }

    .btn {
      min-height: 44px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.6rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 999px; font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 600;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, background 180ms ease, color 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--color-primary); color: white; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-hover); }
    .btn-secondary { background: var(--color-surface); color: var(--color-text); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
    .btn-ghost { border: 1px solid var(--color-border); color: var(--color-text); }
    .theme-toggle {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: var(--color-surface);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
    }

    .hero { padding-top: clamp(var(--space-10), 9vw, 6rem); }
    .hero-grid {
      display: grid; gap: var(--space-8); align-items: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-2xl); line-height: 0.96; letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 10ch; margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    }
    .hero p { color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 58ch; }
    .hero-actions, .cta-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-6); }
    .hero-facts {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-8);
    }
    .fact-card {
      padding: var(--space-4); background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .fact-card strong { display: block; font-size: 1.3rem; font-family: var(--font-display); }
    .fact-card span { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }

    .hero-panel {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 88%, transparent), var(--color-surface));
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: var(--space-5); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .mock-window {
      border-radius: 1.2rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: var(--color-bg);
    }
    .window-bar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.9rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); background: var(--color-surface);
    }
    .dot { width: 0.7rem; height: 0.7rem; border-radius: 999px; background: #f87171; }
    .dot:nth-child(2) { background: #fbbf24; }
    .dot:nth-child(3) { background: #34d399; }
    .code-grid { display: grid; gap: var(--space-4); padding: var(--space-4); }
    .code-card {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-4);
    }
    .code-label { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
    .code-line {
      height: 0.7rem; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary-soft), transparent);
      margin-top: 0.9rem;
    }
    .code-line:nth-child(2) { width: 90%; }
    .code-line:nth-child(3) { width: 72%; }
    .code-line:nth-child(4) { width: 84%; }

    .trust-bar {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-8);
    }
    .trust-item {
      padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .trust-item strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .trust-item span { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }

    .grid-2, .grid-3 { display: grid; gap: var(--space-4); }
    .card {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
      padding: var(--space-5); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); height: 100%;
    }
    .card h3 { font-size: var(--text-lg); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
    .card p, .card li { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .list { list-style: none; display: grid; gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-4); }
    .list li { display: flex; gap: var(--space-3); align-items: flex-start; }
    .check {
      flex: 0 0 auto; width: 1.35rem; height: 1.35rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--color-primary-soft); color: var(--color-primary); display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;
    }

    .curriculum-card { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .module-num {
      display: inline-flex; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; border-radius: 999px; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 700; background: var(--color-primary-soft); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }
    .meta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--space-2); margin-top: var(--space-4); }
    .chip {
      padding: 0.45rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 999px; font-size: var(--text-xs); background: var(--color-surface-2);
      color: var(--color-text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .highlight {
      display: grid; gap: var(--space-4); background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent), #1e293b);
      color: #f8fafc; border-radius: calc(var(--radius-xl) + 0.3rem); padding: clamp(var(--space-6), 6vw, var(--space-10));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .highlight p { color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.8); }
    .highlight .chip { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: white; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

    .instructor {
      display: grid; gap: var(--space-5); align-items: center;
    }
    .instructor-visual {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-surface-2), var(--color-surface));
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); padding: var(--space-6);
      min-height: 320px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .avatar {
      width: 6rem; height: 6rem; border-radius: 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), #38bdf8);
      display: grid; place-items: center; color: white; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }
    .quote {
      position: relative; padding: var(--space-5); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); background: var(--color-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .quote p { font-size: var(--text-base); color: var(--color-text); }
    .quote footer { margin-top: var(--space-4); color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); }

    .pricing {
      display: grid; gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    .price-box {
      padding: clamp(var(--space-5), 5vw, var(--space-8)); border-radius: var(--radius-xl); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      background: var(--color-surface); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .price {
      display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: var(--space-2); margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-2);
      font-family: var(--font-display);
    }
    .price strong { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1; }
    .price span { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .form {
      display: grid; gap: var(--space-3); margin-top: var(--space-5);
    }
    .field { display: grid; gap: 0.45rem; }
    .field label { font-size: var(--text-sm); font-weight: 600; }
    .field input, .field select {
      min-height: 48px; width: 100%; padding: 0.9rem 1rem; border-radius: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      background: var(--color-bg);
    }
    .note { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); }

    .faq-list { display: grid; gap: var(--space-3); }
    details {
      background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    }
    summary {
      cursor: pointer; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--space-3);
    }
    summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    details p { margin-top: var(--space-3); color: var(--color-text-muted); }

    .final-cta {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }

    .site-footer {
      padding: var(--space-8) 0 calc(var(--space-8) + 4.5rem); color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    .mobile-sticky {
      position: fixed; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; z-index: 50; padding: 0.8rem 1rem max(0.8rem, env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 88%, transparent); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .mobile-sticky .btn { width: 100%; }

    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .nav-links { display: flex; }
      .hero-grid, .instructor, .pricing, .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .trust-bar { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .mobile-sticky { display: none; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 759px) {
      .nav .btn-secondary { display: none; }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
      * { transition: none !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

  <header class="site-header" id="top">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="Bootcamp home">
        <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M4 7h16M7 4v6m10-6v6M5 12l7 6 7-6"></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span>CodeLaunch Bootcamp</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
        <a href="#curriculum">Curriculum</a>
        <a href="#outcomes">Outcomes</a>
        <a href="#mentor">Instructor</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Fees</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="nav-actions">
        <button class="theme-toggle" type="button" data-theme-toggle aria-label="Toggle color theme">
          <span aria-hidden="true">◐</span>
        </button>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#pricing">Download Syllabus</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#apply">Apply Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero section">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Live cohort starts 20 May</span>
          <h1>Become a job-ready web developer in 12 weeks.</h1>
          <p>Build real projects with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Git, APIs, and deployment tools. Learn live from mentors, strengthen your portfolio, and prepare for internships or entry-level developer roles.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#apply">Apply Now</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#curriculum">Download Syllabus</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-facts" aria-label="Quick facts">
            <article class="fact-card">
              <strong>12 weeks</strong>
              <span>Weekend + evening live classes</span>
            </article>
            <article class="fact-card">
              <strong>5 projects</strong>
              <span>Portfolio-first, mentor reviewed</span>
            </article>
            <article class="fact-card">
              <strong>Hybrid</strong>
              <span>Online live + recorded support</span>
            </article>
            <article class="fact-card">
              <strong>Career prep</strong>
              <span>Resume, mock interviews, placement support</span>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero-panel" aria-label="Bootcamp preview">
          <div class="mock-window">
            <div class="window-bar">
              <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="code-grid">
              <div class="code-card">
                <div class="code-label">Module 01 — Foundations</div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="code-card">
                <div class="code-label">Project — Responsive landing page</div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="code-card">
                <div class="code-label">Career sprint — Resume + GitHub polish</div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
                <div class="code-line"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-bar" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <div class="trust-item"><strong>4.8/5</strong><span>Learner rating</span></div>
            <div class="trust-item"><strong>1,200+</strong><span>Alumni community</span></div>
            <div class="trust-item"><strong>10+</strong><span>Live coding sessions</span></div>
            <div class="trust-item"><strong>1:1</strong><span>Mock interview support</span></div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="curriculum">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Curriculum</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">What students will build and learn.</h2>
        <p class="section-copy">The structure below keeps the page focused on outcomes while still showing a clear module-by-module path for beginners and career switchers.</p>

        <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
          <article class="card curriculum-card">
            <span class="module-num">1</span>
            <h3>HTML, CSS, and responsive design</h3>
            <p>Learn layout systems, semantic markup, flexbox, grid, accessibility basics, and mobile-first page building.</p>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="chip">2 weeks</span><span class="chip">Project: landing page</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="card curriculum-card">
            <span class="module-num">2</span>
            <h3>JavaScript fundamentals and DOM</h3>
            <p>Understand variables, functions, arrays, async basics, events, form handling, and UI interactions.</p>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="chip">2 weeks</span><span class="chip">Project: interactive app</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="card curriculum-card">
            <span class="module-num">3</span>
            <h3>React, components, and state</h3>
            <p>Build reusable interfaces, manage data flow, use hooks, and create polished front-end applications.</p>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="chip">3 weeks</span><span class="chip">Project: dashboard UI</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="card curriculum-card">
            <span class="module-num">4</span>
            <h3>Git, GitHub, APIs, and deployment</h3>
            <p>Work like a developer with version control, fetch APIs, debugging workflows, and Vercel or Netlify deployment.</p>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="chip">2 weeks</span><span class="chip">Project: API app</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="card curriculum-card">
            <span class="module-num">5</span>
            <h3>Capstone portfolio project</h3>
            <p>Create a complete portfolio-ready project with mentor reviews, documentation, and presentation feedback.</p>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="chip">2 weeks</span><span class="chip">Demo day</span></div>
          </article>
          <article class="card curriculum-card">
            <span class="module-num">6</span>
            <h3>Career readiness sprint</h3>
            <p>Polish resume, LinkedIn, GitHub, communication skills, and interview answers for internships and junior roles.</p>
            <div class="meta-row"><span class="chip">1 week</span><span class="chip">Mock interviews</span></div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="outcomes">
      <div class="container grid-2">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Outcomes</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Sell the future result, not just the topics.</h2>
          <p class="section-copy">This section turns the course into a career promise by emphasizing portfolio strength, confidence, mentorship, and job readiness.</p>
